caption:
Hosted the annual @runngun.studios dj set in Santa Teresa with a group of strangers and digital nomads.
Being in Costa Rica for a few weeks inspired both @lucasgaugerr and I. What went from a dopamine detox trip turned into an experience with the most genuine people we have met. We wanted to spread this community with the people in Santa Teresa showcasing how important human connection is. This moment will live with us forever, can’t wait till next time.
FULL SET now live on YouTube @ RunNGunUSA 
Thank you to everyone who helped put this together 🖤

